---
title: Tiger Prawn Risotto with Asparagus and Dukkah
description: This warming and hearty Prawn Risotto with Asparagus is bursting full of flavours and makes the perfect dinner night option, from HelloFresh.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tiger-prawn-risotto-1af21266-3c6d9d75.jpg
